VALUES(25,'Miss Dior',150,5,'women',3,50,'elegant','Eau de Perfume','night','aspring','Poze/MissDior.jpg','rosemary,lily,liliac','Miss Dior was first launched in 1947, as part of Christian Dior`s presentation of his first couture collection. The scent became an immediate must-have for women around the world, and still holds its place as one of the most popular perfumes on the market. The elegant, luxurious packaging makes it a true classic, as well as the fragrance’s fresh, citrusy scent, which contains notes of Italian mandarin, Egyptian jasmine and Indonesian patchouli.');
