VALUES(26,'Balenciaga Paris',200,5,'women',8,100,'elegant','Eau de Perfume','night','autumn','Poze/Balenciaga.jpg','rosemary,lily,liliac','A fully fragranced perfume, Balenciaga Paris is the perfect pick if you really want to make a scent statement. It contains strong, sexy notes of mossy wood, violet leaf, pepper, cedarwood, patchouli and vetiver. Plus, the blown-glass bottle`s creative design is reminiscent of the fashion label`s inimitable style');
